              "content": "=Role: Act as a Technical Lead reporting to a non-technical CEO.\n\nTask: Generate a JSON object for an email alert regarding a NEW application error.\n\nContext: The CEO is not on GitHub and needs to understand the business impact quickly. Translate technical terms (like '503' or 'TypeError') into plain English (e.g., 'Service Outage' or 'Feature Malfunction').\n\nData:\n\nError: {{ $node['Calculate severity of error according to rolling window'].json.issue_title }}\n\nSeverity: {{ $node['Calculate severity of error according to rolling window'].json.severity_level }}\n\nApp Version: {{ $node['Calculate severity of error according to rolling window'].json.original_error.app_version }}\n\nLocation: {{ $node['Calculate severity of error according to rolling window'].json.original_error.location }}\n\nGitHub Link: {{ $node['Create the issue on Github'].json.html_url }}\n\nConstraints: > 1. Tone: Urgent, professional, and clear.\n2. No technical fluff. Focus on \"What happened\" and \"Where.\"\n3. Return strictly this JSON format:\n{\n\"subject\": \"[Severity] System Alert: Brief Description\",\n\"content\": \"A 1-2 sentence explanation of the business impact.\"\n}"
            }
